<dita>
   <concept id="FAR_14_201_6" class="- topic/topic concept/concept " xtrc="">
      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph class="- topic/ph " props="autonumber">14.201-6</ph> Solicitation provisions.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
         <ol id="d792e13" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d819e10">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
						            The provisions prescribed in this subsection apply to preparation and submission of bids in general. See other FAR parts for provisions and clauses related to specific acquisition requirements.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d819e15">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  
						            Insert in all invitations for bids the provisions at-</p>
               <ol id="d792e32" class="- topic/ol ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d819e21">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        <xref href="52.214-3.dita#FAR_52_214_3"
                              base="i1059877"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">52.214-3</xref>, Amendments to Invitations For Bids; and</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d819e28">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        <xref href="52.214-4.dita#FAR_52_214_4"
                              base="i1059887"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">52.214-4</xref>, False Statements in Bids.</p>
                  </li>
               </ol>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d819e35">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(c)</ph>
                  
						            Insert the following provisions in invitations for bids:</p>
               <ol id="d792e68" class="- topic/ol ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d819e41">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        <xref href="52.214-5.dita#FAR_52_214_5"
                              base="i1059897"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">52.214-5</xref>, Submission of Bids.</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d819e48">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        <xref href="52.214-6.dita#FAR_52_214_6"
                              base="i1059912"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">52.214-6</xref>, Explanation to Prospective Bidders.</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d819e55">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(3)</ph>
                        <xref href="52.214-7.dita#FAR_52_214_7"
                              base="i1059921"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">52.214-7</xref>, Late Submissions, Modifications, and Withdrawals of Bids.</p>
                  </li>
               </ol>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d819e62">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(d)</ph>
                  
						            [Reserved]</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d819e67">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(e)</ph>
                  
						            Insert in all invitations for bids, except those for construction, the provisions at <xref href="52.214-10.dita#FAR_52_214_10"
                        base="i1059942"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.214-10</xref>, Contract Award-Sealed Bidding.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d819e75">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(f)</ph>
                  
						            Insert in invitations for bids to which the uniform contract format applies, the provision at <xref href="52.214-12.dita#FAR_52_214_12"
                        base="i1059959"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.214-12</xref>, Preparation of Bids.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d819e83">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(g)</ph>
                  
						            [Reserved]</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d819e88">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(h)</ph>
                  
						            Insert the provision at <xref href="52.214-14.dita#FAR_52_214_14"
                        base="i1059991"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.214-14</xref>, Place of Performance-Sealed Bidding, in invitations for bids except those in which the place of performance is specified by the government.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d819e96">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(i)</ph>
                  
						            Insert the provision at <xref href="52.214-15.dita#FAR_52_214_15"
                        base="i1060026"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.214-15</xref>, Period for Acceptance of Bids, in invitations for bids (IFB’s) that are not issued on <xref href="https://www.gsa.gov/forms-library/solicitation-offer-and-award"
                        format="html"
                        scope="external"
                        class="- topic/xref ">SF 33</xref> or <xref href="https://www.gsa.gov/forms-library/solicitationcontract"
                        format="html"
                        scope="external"
                        class="- topic/xref ">SF 1447</xref> except IFB’s-</p>
               <ol id="d792e180" class="- topic/ol ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d819e111">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        
								                For construction work; or</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d819e116">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        
								                In which the government specifies a minimum acceptance period.</p>
                  </li>
               </ol>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d819e121">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(j)</ph>
                  
						            Insert the provision at <xref href="52.214-16.dita#FAR_52_214_16"
                        base="i1060035"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.214-16</xref>, Minimum Bid Acceptance Period, in invitations for bids, except for construction, if the contracting officer determines that a minimum acceptance period must be specified.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d819e129">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(k)</ph>
                  
						            [Reserved]</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d819e135">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(l)</ph>
                  
						            Insert the provision at <xref href="52.214-18.dita#FAR_52_214_18"
                        base="i1060053"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.214-18</xref>, Preparation of Bids-Construction, in invitations for bids for construction work.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d819e143">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(m)</ph>
                  
						            Insert the provision at <xref href="52.214-19.dita#FAR_52_214_19"
                        base="i1060071"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.214-19</xref>, Contract Award-Sealed Bidding-Construction, in all invitations for bids for construction work.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d819e151">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(n)</ph>
                  
						            [Reserved]</p>
            </li>
            <li props="Runin" class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d819e156">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(o)</ph>
               </p>
               <ol id="d792e265" class="- topic/ol ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d819e161">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        
								                Insert the provision at <xref href="52.214-20.dita#FAR_52_214_20"
                              base="i1060083"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">52.214-20</xref>, Bid Samples, in invitations for bids if bid samples are required.</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d819e169">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        
								                If it appears that the conditions in <xref href="14.202-4.dita#FAR_14_202_4"
                              base="i1110737"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">14.202-4</xref>(e)(1) will apply and the contracting officer anticipates granting waivers and-</p>
                     <ol id="d792e290" class="- topic/ol ">
                        <li class="- topic/li ">
                           <p class="- topic/p " id="d819e178">
                              <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(i)</ph>
                              
										                    If the nature of the required product does not necessitate limiting the grant of a waiver to a product produced at the same plant in which the product previously acquired or tested was produced, use the provision with its Alternate I; or</p>
                        </li>
                        <li class="- topic/li ">
                           <p class="- topic/p " id="d819e183">
                              <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(ii)</ph>
                              
										                    If the nature of the required product necessitates limiting the grant of a waiver to a product produced at the same plant in which the product previously acquired or tested was produced, use the provision with its Alternate II.</p>
                        </li>
                     </ol>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d819e188">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(3)</ph>
                        
								                See <xref href="14.202-4.dita#FAR_14_202_4"
                              base="i1110737"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">14.202-4</xref>(e)(2) regarding waiving the requirement for all bidders.</p>
                  </li>
               </ol>
            </li>
            <li props="Runin" class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d819e196">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(p)</ph>
               </p>
               <ol id="d792e334" class="- topic/ol ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d819e201">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        
								                Insert the provision at <xref href="52.214-21.dita#FAR_52_214_21"
                              base="i1060114"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">52.214-21</xref>, Descriptive Literature, in invitations for bids if-</p>
                     <ol id="d792e347" class="- topic/ol ">
                        <li class="- topic/li ">
                           <p class="- topic/p " id="d819e210">
                              <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(i)</ph>
                              
										                    Descriptive literature is required to evaluate the technical acceptability of an offered product; and</p>
                        </li>
                        <li class="- topic/li ">
                           <p class="- topic/p " id="d819e215">
                              <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(ii)</ph>
                              
										                    The required information will not be readily available unless it is submitted by bidders.</p>
                        </li>
                     </ol>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d819e220">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        
								                Use the basic clause with its Alternate I if the possibility exists that the contracting officer may waive the requirement for furnishing descriptive literature for a bidder offering a previously supplied product that meets specification requirements of the current solicitation.</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d819e225">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(3)</ph>
                        
								                See <xref href="14.202-5.dita#FAR_14_202_5"
                              base="i1110770"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">14.202-5</xref>(d)(2) regarding waiving the requirement for all bidders.</p>
                  </li>
               </ol>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d819e233">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(q)</ph>
                  
						            Insert the provision at <xref href="52.214-22.dita#FAR_52_214_22"
                        base="i1060145"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.214-22</xref>, Evaluation of Bids for Multiple Awards, in invitations for bids if the contracting officer determines that multiple awards might be made if doing so is economically advantageous to the government.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d819e241">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(r)</ph>
                  
						            Insert the provision at <xref href="52.214-23.dita#FAR_52_214_23"
                        base="i1060154"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.214-23</xref>, Late Submissions, Modifications, Revisions, and Withdrawals of Technical Proposals Under Two-Step Sealed Bidding, in solicitations for technical proposals in step one of two-step sealed bidding.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d819e249">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(s)</ph>
                  
						            Insert the provision at <xref href="52.214-24.dita#FAR_52_214_24"
                        base="i1060180"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.214-24</xref>, Multiple Technical Proposals, in solicitations for technical proposals in step one of two-step sealed bidding if the contracting officer permits the submission of multiple technical proposals.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d819e257">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(t)</ph>
                  
						            Insert the provision at <xref href="52.214-25.dita#FAR_52_214_25"
                        base="i1060189"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.214-25</xref>, Step Two of Two-Step Sealed Bidding, in invitations for bids issued under step two of two-step sealed bidding.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d819e265">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(u)</ph>
                  
						            [Reserved]</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d819e270">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(v)</ph>
                  
						            Insert the provision at <xref href="52.214-31.dita#FAR_52_214_31"
                        base="i1060334"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.214-31</xref>, Facsimile Bids, in solicitations if facsimile bids are authorized (see <xref href="14.202-7.dita#FAR_14_202_7"
                        base="i1110799"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">14.202-7</xref>).</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d819e282">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(w)</ph>
                  
						            Insert the provision at <xref href="52.214-34.dita#FAR_52_214_34"
                        base="i1060360"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.214-34</xref>, Submission of Offers in the English Language, in solicitations that include any of the clauses prescribed in <xref href="25.1101.dita#FAR_25_1101"
                        base="i1090819"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">25.1101</xref> or <xref href="25.1102.dita#FAR_25_1102"
                        base="i1090904"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">25.1102</xref>. It may be included in other solicitations when the contracting officer decides that it is necessary.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d819e296">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(x)</ph>
                  
						            Insert the provision at <xref href="52.214-35.dita#FAR_52_214_35"
                        base="i1060369"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.214-35</xref>, Submission of Offers in U.S. Currency, in solicitations that include any of the clauses prescribed in <xref href="25.1101.dita#FAR_25_1101"
                        base="i1090819"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">25.1101</xref> or <xref href="25.1102.dita#FAR_25_1102"
                        base="i1090904"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">25.1102</xref>, unless the contracting officer includes the clause at <xref href="52.225-17.dita#FAR_52_225_17"
                        base="i1054275"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.225-17</xref>, Evaluation of Foreign Currency Offers, as prescribed in <xref href="25.1103.dita#FAR_25_1103"
                        base="i1090971"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">25.1103</xref>(d). It may be included in other solicitations when the contracting officer decides that it is necessary.</p>
            </li>
         </ol>
      </conbody>
   </concept>
</dita>
